The paper discusses an algorithm that learns from a set of examples using neural networks and genetic operators. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks also suggests the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of domain-specific knowledge, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
